Package: quickgeo
Title: Quick Zonal Statistics of Global Point Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Shan",
           family = "Ye",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "yeshanumich@126.com")
Maintainer: Shan Ye <yeshanumich@126.com>
Description: Quickly conduct zonal statistics of point data and visualize the result on a world map. A raster file of the statistics is also generated. Good for exploratory analysis of spatial data in global or continental scales.
